Author: scaredyk4t
Text: I feel this hard. I’ll wash and put away any dishes I use to make whatever I’m eating especially if I’m binging so my roommate/best friend won’t see even though she literally does not care at all. Like she prolly wants to see that I’m actually eating.   I count out grapes, blueberries, peanuts, etc.   I make food super spicy and hot in temp so it takes me longer to eat it.  I reaaaally wish I had a scale for food.
